snippet.title: Monster DNA: Project Announce
snippet.description:
Welcome to the lab...
Super Rare Originals, in collaboration with CH757 and Key, is excited to unveil our upcoming project Monster DNA; a single-player psychological horror game where you create deadly monsters for mysterious clients. But beware… your creations might be the death of you. In this twisted lab, survival depends on your wits. One wrong move, and you could be their next victim.
